creator: Cloud Payments
descriptionHtml:
The Fundz app allows you to manage your funds in a contacless manner and conduct digital transactions for numerous activities in your day-to-day life. Check out all the great features available that we are sure you'll love...

SEND AND REQUEST MONEY
• Create an account with an email address, bank account, or credit/debit card and start using the Fundz app.
• Use your QR code to send or request money right away with Fundz.
• Search by email address to find the person you’re looking for.
• Fundz keeps track of all your incoming, outgoing, and pending transactions.

SHARED FUNDZ
• Create a monetary fund for dinners with friends, fundraisers, community projects or any other event.
• Invite friends, family, or colleagues to participate in your fund by easily and securely sending money within the app.
• Contribute to funds you have been invited to with just a few taps.
• Track the progress and see contributions to your funds until you’ve reached your goal.
• Use the fund QR code to invite others in.

CASH OUT
• You can withdraw money from your balance to your bank account any time you want.
• Link multiple cards and bank accounts to your Fundz app.
• You can load digital balances using a credit/debit card or directly from your bank account.

NOTIFICATIONS
• Receive push notifications so you won't miss any transaction or invitation.
descriptionShort: An application designed for all communities to gather share or raise Funds.
